data.description: This meticulously kept 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home backs up to a green belt and is at the end of a Cul-De-Sac; boasts an open and airy floor plan with neutral colors throughout. Lot's of windows that provide plenty of natural light. Curved entryways, ceramic tile flooring, and a niche in the entryway all provide character to this charming home! Recessed lighting in the kitchen, lengthy breakfast bar, glass tile back splash with lots of counter top space and cabinets. Great sized rooms, closets and bathrooms. Well kept HUGE backyard with mature trees, wood privacy and metal fencing, a cement slab patio and a ton of room for entertaining and/or outdoor activities!  Roof was replaced 11/7/2023, HVAC is a little over 2 year sold, Water Heater is a little over 1 year old. Minutes from 281 and 1604! Close to schools, entertainment and shopping.
